Description:
Investors, Watch Your Money Grow!
Investors take note! Don't lift a finger, sit back and watch you money grow when you invest in this solid 5 bedroom home in Corio already tenanted with the same reliable tenants for the past 4 years, this easy to maintain two storey home is the perfect addition to any portfolio.
Entering the home from the double carport you will be greeted by an inviting carpeted lounge with the polished timber stair case on your left and open study/work space. Stepping through you will walk into the tiled dining/kitchen area equipped with gas hotplates, electric wall oven, dishwasher, pantry, ample bench and cupboard space.
The huge master bedroom with built in robes opens out onto a private courtyard, perfect for any parent to sit back and relax. A second bedroom and bathroom are located close by. Upstairs are an additional three good sized bedrooms all carpeted with built in robes and a second bathroom and separate toilet.
Outside the home has shaded entertaining area for family BBQ's, a secure backyard with established gardens where kids and pets can safely play and an additional lock up colour bond garage. Extra features of this home include Air conditioning and plenty of extra storage.
Receiving $340 rental return a week with the tenants on a secure lease until May 2018, this is a fantastic investment where your retirement will reap the rewards.
Insights: 155 Princess Road, Corio VIC 3214 was last sold in 2017 and 2 other 5 bedroom house in Corio have recently been sold.

Description:
Fantastic family living.
Set on a generous 530m2 allotment in a quiet court location is this fantastic family home with a very accommodating floor plan. A great opportunity for a young couple to get into the market, a fabulous family home or perfect addition to your investment portfolio! Featuring 4 bedrooms in total all with BIR's, while the master comes complete with WIR & own ensuite. Enjoy the 2 large open plan living areas with central dining and light filled kitchen with views of the rear yard. The neat family sized bathroom lies towards the back of the property located next to an additional powder room & separate laundry. Outside boasts an impressive fully enclosed alfresco area perfect for seamless indoor/outdoor entertaining all year round as well as an additional bungalow and grassed area perfect for pets or kids to enjoy. Parking isn't an issue with a large 2 way access driveway & single lock up garage with rear roller door access to the backyard pergola. An opportunity not to be missed in an ideal location, close to schools, shops, shopping centre, medical facilities & easy access to the Geelong Ring Road & freeway.

Description:
Spacious House in Ideal Position For Easy Family Living
What is excellent about a place like this, is that it is close to every community facility key to convenient living... shops, schools, swimming pool, library, medical facilities, and the list goes on. The lovely 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom solid brick residence provides a functional floor plan with separate living spaces thoughtfully positioned at either end of the home, an upper level master bedroom complete with an updated ensuite + study and a central and practical timber kitchen.
Walk out onto a generous (partially decked and covered) back yard, securely fenced with double gate access from the front to the oversized single powered garage, + a secure garden/tool shed for additional storage space... and room for the beloved family pet of course!
Not only is this the ideal investment property, it's the perfect place for a big family to proudly call home... this will be hot on the market, don't miss your chance!

Description:
Fully Renovated - Ready to move in!
If you're looking for a fresh start then this spacious, fully renovated 2BR home in Corio is just the place to provide you with a comfortable and convenient lifestyle. Comprising of a spacious main lounge at the entrance with floorboards throughout the property. Spotless kitchen with stainless steel oven/range hood, dishwasher & meals area. A gleaming central bathroom which has been recently re-tiled, 2 generous bedrooms and a practical laundry towards the back door. Situated on a grand 659m2 approx. allotment the property provides a large rear yard & double tandem garage. Only minutes' walk to the Corio shopping Centre, this charming home provides easy access to all major amenities. Perfect for first home buyers, investors and developers (STCA) alike - this property won't last long!

Description:
Great First Home or Investment Opportunity
Whether you are buying your first home or adding to your property investment portfolio look no further!
As soon as you walk through the stained glass front door on to the good quality timber flooring, you know this property is something special.
It boasts a good size lounge, kitchen with dishwasher, 3 bedrooms (2 with bir) and ducted heating and a/c.
There is ample space with an undercover outside area, plus a fully lined room outside ideal for a second living room, kids retreat or secure storage area.
This delightful property has 1 small sheds, and 1 large shed with car accommodation for 2 cars, complete with roller shutters on the outside windows.
Currently tenanted to long term tenants at $250 p/w

Low Maintenance Living!
